name: The Adventures of DJ Khaled
body:
###The Adventures of DJ Khaled
So I recently attended a programming event called "CodeDay" hosted in Seattle and this was the game that I made. It's a very simple and silly game. If time permits, I might make some bug fixes and add some more features such as:

-Different difficulties

-Hit points for minions

-Jet Ski stage

-Cocoa Butter

and etc.

Here's the link: 

https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/107306189/DJKHALED/index.html

Enjoy! :)
